{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_017mdmiX1rAFt9uWNjs5Q7gz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Commit successful. Here's a summary of what was implemented for US-014:\n\n## US-014 - Full SPH simulation loop with rendering\n\n### New files:\n- **`fallingsand3d/simulation.py`** - SPH simulation orchestrator class with:\n  - Full pipeline per substep: hash -> argsort -> fused_reorder -> build -> step1 -> step2 -> integrate\n  - Sim/render decoupling: `sim_steps = clamp(round(speed * wall_dt / sim_dt), 0, max_substeps)`\n  - `speed` parameter (default 1.0) with `adjust_speed(delta)` clamped to [0.1, 10.0]\n  - `max_substeps = 20` to prevent spiral-of-death\n  - Constant memory uploaded to all 6 kernel modules at init\n  - Pre-allocated grid cell tables reused every frame\n  - `copy_to_vbos()` copies UNSORTED pos/color to mapped GL VBOs\n  - Pause/resume via `toggle_pause()`\n\n### Modified files:\n- **`fallingsand3d/main.py`** - Rewritten to integrate simulation:\n  - Initial scene: ~8K water cube at (0, 0.5, 0) + ~8K sand bed at y=-0.5 to -0.3\n  - Keyboard: Space=pause, R=reset, +/-=speed, Esc=quit\n  - Title bar shows: particle count, FPS, substep count, speed, pause state\n  - VBO copy once per frame after all substeps\n  - PTX workaround applied before any CuPy compilation\n\n### Acceptance criteria met:\n- All .cu kernels loaded via CuPy RawModule with `--use_fast_math` and `-I` include path\n- GridParams, SimParams, MaterialProps, Interactions uploaded to constant memory at init\n- Sim/render decoupled with speed parameter and substep budget\n- Pipeline ordering: hash -> argsort -> fused_reorder -> build -> step1 -> step2 -> integrate\n- Rendering happens ONCE per frame (copy UNSORTED pos/color to VBO -> draw)\n- Space bar pauses/resumes, R resets, +/- adjusts speed\n\n<promise>COMPLETE</promise>"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":27